            "en": "<p>You must pay the one-off fee for the application for recognition as a drilling company.</p><ul><li>For <strong>2021</strong>, the one-off fee is <strong>586 </strong>euros.</li><li>For an application in <strong>2022</strong>, the one-off fee is <strong>606 </strong>euros.</li><li>In <strong>2021</strong>, the one-off fee is <strong>147 </strong>euros for each additional discipline. In <strong>2022</strong>, <strong>152 </strong>euros.</li><li>These sums are index-adjusted every year.</li></ul><p>As a recognised drilling company, you must pay the <a href=\"https://www.uat-vlaanderen.be/vlarel-retributies\">annual fee</a> for the supervision of the recognition. You will receive an invoice for this by post at the start of the calendar year in your name at your official address.</p><ul><li>For <strong>2022 </strong>the annual fee amounts to EUR <strong>121</strong>.</li><li>For <strong>2022 </strong>the annual fee amounts to EUR <strong>30 </strong>for each additional discipline.</li><li>These sums are index-adjusted every year.</li></ul>"
