        "en": "<p>Companies that perform certain work in the Flemish Region on stationary fire protection equipment with fluorinated greenhouse gases or substances that deplete the ozone layer, where there is a risk of emissions of these harmful substances, require a Flemish recognition. This covers the installation, maintenance, repair and decommissioning of such equipment.</p><p><a href=\"https://datasets.omgeving.vlaanderen.be/be.vl.omgeving.erkenningen.distribution.bedrijven_brandbeveiligingsapparatuur.pdf\">Download the overview list of recognised fire protection equipment companies</a>.</p>",
