        "en": "<p>You require a Flemish recognition as an inspection body for the inspection of refrigeration companies. Such an inspection body assesses whether the company meets the Flemish recognition conditions for a refrigeration company. If the refrigeration company satisfies all the recognition conditions. the inspection body will issue a European certificate and a Flemish recognition certificate to the business.</p><p>Both the refrigeration technician and the refrigeration company require Flemish recognition if they want to perform activities in the Flemish Region on stationary refrigeration installations with fluorinated greenhouse gases or substances that deplete the ozone layer.</p><p> </p>"
